<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Letter of Recommendation</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .institution-name { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .institution-details { font-size: 12px; color: #333; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .document-title {
            font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #000;
            text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .date-section { margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 14px; }
        .body-text { font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; margin: 18px 0; line-height: 1.9; }
        .info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 18px 0; font-size: 13px; }
        .info-table td { padding: 8px 10px; border: 1px solid #999; }
        .info-table td.lbl { font-weight: bold; width: 30%; background-color: #f0f0f0; }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
        }
        .signature-block { text-align: center; }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 2px solid #000;
            margin-top: 55px;
            padding-top: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- HEADER -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="institution-name">{{institutionName}}</div>
            <div class="institution-details">{{institutionAddress}}</div>
            <div class="institution-details">Phone: {{institutionPhone}} | Email: {{institutionEmail}}</div>
            <div class="document-title">Letter of Recommendation</div>
        </div>

        <!-- DATE -->
        <div class="date-section">
            <strong>Date:</strong> {{issueDate}}
        </div>

        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><strong>TO WHOMSOEVER IT MAY CONCERN</strong></p>

        <!-- BODY -->
        <div class="body-text">
            <p>It is my pleasure to recommend <strong>{{studentName}}</strong>, Enrollment No. <strong>{{enrollmentNo}}</strong>, a student of the <strong>{{branch}}</strong> department at <strong>{{institutionName}}</strong>, for the purpose of <strong>{{applyingFor}}</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <table class="info-table">
            <tr><td class="lbl">Student Name</td><td>{{studentName}}</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="lbl">Enrollment No.</td><td>{{enrollmentNo}}</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="lbl">Branch / Department</td><td>{{branch}}</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="lbl">Academic Year</td><td>{{academicYear}}</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="lbl">CGPA</td><td>{{cgpa}}</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="lbl">Applying For</td><td>{{applyingFor}}</td></tr>
            {{#if targetUniversity}}
            <tr><td class="lbl">Target University / Program</td><td>{{targetUniversity}}</td></tr>
            {{/if}}
        </table>

        <div class="body-text">
            <p>During their time at {{institutionName}}, {{studentName}} has demonstrated commendable academic diligence and a strong work ethic. Based on my interactions and their academic performance, I am confident that they possess the qualities, skills, and determination necessary to excel in their chosen endeavor.</p>
        </div>

        {{#if achievements}}
        <div class="body-text">
            <p><strong>Notable Achievements / Remarks:</strong><br>{{achievements}}</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="body-text">
            <p>I wholeheartedly recommend <strong>{{studentName}}</strong> and believe they will be a valuable addition. I am available for any further queries at <strong>{{institutionEmail}}</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- SIGNATURES -->
        <div class="signature-section">
            <div class="signature-block">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 55px;"></div>
                <div class="signature-line">
                    {{hodName}}<br>
                    <span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:11px;">Head of Department</span><br>
                    <span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:11px;">{{institutionName}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-block">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 55px;"></div>
                <div class="signature-line">
                    {{deanName}}<br>
                    <span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:11px;">Dean / Director</span><br>
                    <span style="font-weight:normal;font-size:11px;">{{institutionName}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FOOTER -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Generated Date: {{generatedDate}}</p>
            <p>Document ID: LOR-{{documentId}}</p>
            <p style="margin-top:8px;font-size:10px;color:#999;">This is a system-generated document. Original signature and institutional seal are required for validity.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
